# Founder's Quest — there is NO server environment, by design.
#
# You found this file looking for the variables to set. There are none, and
# none should ever be added:
#
#   - There is no ANTHROPIC_API_KEY. The game is BYOK (bring your own key):
#     each player enters their OWN Anthropic API key at runtime, in the
#     Council temple, in their browser. It is stored device-side under its
#     own storage key, never serialized into saves, never exported, and the
#     browser talks to api.anthropic.com directly — no server sits in that
#     path, so no server needs a key.
#
#   - There is no analytics/telemetry endpoint, no database URL, no session
#     secret. The deploy is a pure static site (Cloudflare Pages, build
#     `npm run build`, output `dist/`, NODE_VERSION=22 — see
#     docs/canon/06-deploy-runbook.md).
#
# If a change ever seems to need a server-side variable, stop and read
# CLAUDE.md and docs/canon/01-constitution.md first: adding one would break
# the game's core privacy promise.
